# Flask To-Do App Upgrade Plan

This plan details the steps to implement user authentication, an improved data model for tasks, a modernized UI using Bootstrap 5, and a reorganized, cleaner project structure.

## Proposed Changes

We will transition the single-file [app.py](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app.py) structure into a more organized Flask application structure.

### Project Structure Restructuring

The new project structure will be:
```
c:/Users/SHAHAB COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo app/
├── app.py                 (Entry point to run the app)
├── requirements.txt       (Dependencies)
├── app/                   (Main application package)
│   ├── __init__.py        (App factory & initializations)
│   ├── models.py          (Database models: User, Todo)
│   ├── routes.py          (All view functions & routing)
│   ├── static/            (Static assets)
│   │   └── style.css
│   └── templates/         (HTML templates)
│       ├── base.html      (Base layout with Bootstrap 5)
│       ├── index.html     (To-Do list view)
│       ├── login.html     (User login form)
│       └── register.html  (User registration form)
```

### Dependencies
#### [MODIFY] [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/requirements.txt)
- Add `Flask-Login` for session management and user authentication.
- Add `email-validator` (optional, if we validate emails, but we will use usernames for simplicity).

### Application Logic & Initializations
#### [NEW] [app/\_\_init\_\_.py](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app/__init__.py)
- Initialize the Flask app, configure `SQLALCHEMY_DATABASE_URI` and a secret key for flask sessions.
- Initialize `Flask-SQLAlchemy` and `Flask-Login`.

#### [DELETE] [app.py](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app.py) (The old single-file app)
#### [NEW] [app.py](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app.py) (The new entry point)
- Will import the `app` instance from `app` package and run it.

### Database Models
#### [NEW] [app/models.py](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app/models.py)
- `User` model: `id`, `username`, `password_hash`. Inherits from `UserMixin`.
- [Todo](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app.py#11-15) model:
  - `id`, `title` -> existing fields.
  - `user_id` -> Foreign Key to `User`.
  - `status` -> String (Pending, In Progress, Completed). Default: Pending.
  - `priority` -> String (Low, Medium, High). Default: Medium.
  - `due_date` -> Date (Optional).

### Routes & Views
#### [NEW] [app/routes.py](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app/routes.py)
- Authentication Routes:
  - `/register`: Handles user registration, uses `werkzeug.security.generate_password_hash`.
  - `/login`: Handles user login, uses `werkzeug.security.check_password_hash`.
  - `/logout`: Handles logging out the user via `flask_login.logout_user`.
- Task Routes (Protected with `@login_required`):
  - `/`: Display user-specific tasks (fetched via `current_user.todos`).
  - `/add`: Handle adding tasks with the new fields (priority, due_date).
  - `/update/<id>`: Full edit page to modify status, title, priority, due date.
  - `/delete/<id>`: Deletes the task.

### UI / Templates
#### [NEW] [app/templates/base.html](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app/templates/base.html)
- Includes Bootstrap 5 via CDN.
- Contains a Navbar for navigation (Home, Login, Register, Logout).
- Renders flash messages block for success/error alerts.

#### [MODIFY] [app/templates/index.html](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app/templates/index.html) (Moved from old templates/)
- Updates the list to display priorities (e.g., as Bootstrap badges), statuses, and due dates.
- Adds appropriate buttons to Edit and Delete.

#### [NEW] [app/templates/login.html](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app/templates/login.html) & [app/templates/register.html](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app/templates/register.html)
- Clean, responsive forms using Bootstrap 5 to register and log in.

#### [NEW] [app/templates/edit.html](file:///c:/Users/SHAHAB%20COMPUTERS/OneDrive/Desktop/ToDo%20app/app/templates/edit.html)
- Form to edit an existing task to change its priority, status, or title.

